ng about the Java helper possibly not being covered. The function `findDescriptors` seems accessible from the Scala test, so is that alright? I wonder if using `scala.tools.reflect.ToolBox` would work, but maybe itâ€™s not the best idea. I should check the stats and dynamic access report for insights!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_02aca925a3c1ad1e0169f3b039550481939f42ae4a39367a54\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp87BI9NMyclYAGJKz2-wJ6jqe6n7R1NpznBELbE_19q1F7UD8M29AO4Kr9-Y4SMsYlhBjeAKyHQRPkMJKQmC0hcYJzbEFPzLWsG5EXyC-JiLV1_RunPEykE6sWHEgMObbvYbzyACjsDrnvlfZfuVMnJUNHobs-R1eF_IIjmyW5dNcetk_Ka24A9t2Roju76gCr9avGrtmVvUOyHkXQ-8fCdNi1AHE89k1gne2v8QHz4wLfe00HCS2Sh7jb45gzP0cKl2dlLARQpeEfbeULfUqecr7NeC620n8WBD0eXfOJEha3ZO6VxuYulkSwvUSiwQJCjs8ict0oCamSW0_lks7a70-egcVo5KYCW_Hil9oKlydYIewTnvEUH4pDYMRgKmHOxYRp4x87JG3cGk5f3dNWjrnau9adXUCjtebqJfXkqIIOhHZ8ScQsCn0XLFEt-z5unSXfEZEn6zvItD9IGm7X_-DmOoxBJ9wqoejH8-gPLmAA5HO5x46v9bdULQYL4vPCAHktYfDdDvWQ8XpnVipgG4Btvc33wdtW-8Q5P9IsJhYZbbdg7e9cbRloUOtoHvQ_eioFQTXVyvte5DceWDOwrCOuAp56Uu-Zzr7SbcOfE7fL9ghD9ZRRmvz9kvo2rokecfEWvtQ0xePqQghAIrIFcuK7lt22x9Lk6vVbb1IjlqpUakp02wBJTVkqYVzjlN-S5WDxmQ2ox02o8iepIlkUBU4x68a6ZXOCpbBm8qFkFz5oOqs3xP0a7XsThlWD6EqPT18wNfguJ8HYLMzwZBRloK20yqYHgljs4zE7e6lKgtcwAOtey85QbIV9LJrUm3veksokKmlu1k11UyOjDY4Ow7bMJ7OPECZlpjLaYCZhWp0MbrvM9c0TZk5gSQnAslXO42ic4MpA3FPj-JKtKLuGtDpObewVCym1ECdodc-v00NiOoIKr49I3laHZL5_FTbfH_ukzbJXSx0QrFYQEF3vHDDSW58B3vBASrXvmTnWNWo_zF4rOCeXA10_0HDe4vPAfNcIS97qmlmB_xVZUlNjh_wz1WWg_AtxJy_YGknEePLoyKBNoLowg9mn0h_fGDbvFJRc4x2RAKwLpzI3I2bNc0HC4ibxadWajRv543z7JjcKqHdU5bLc7ZtqfJzkZc6072jUZx4GZp1cHkOmY_iahdlyQFvWqm0p03UdXeKTjfjA7HLeeThaSvvSF0fGpKSb4sETdnmYA5TZB0279SBwgpkaOdgsYheonshVypz5ajAEPH-Kbf6UsTRa0gz4jgo1LBB5ZCU3_mrzb-PF-d8pDJCXIt3hKZt8TGk3LXZ-M5lWmrCB0e6bwYw7KJcBRLAdPgT9pIrxMYlc2tNs2x23sSl2_4bM5P6fWgY8x9-WEriPbnSG5pZmmGlAOuBoK4CSXjmRlag9FuwMwRwm3HnlxENBU83xNVZ1vROLsXkOtcZmNeAFJDxrXl7o4e6eT9zbgV3qabOsXfcDKWNgHsNA18vPsTNyrljnu3QsEwievp3xuIwc55dXqFdMxg32_O0ILh7_LU5Nx404FBz